fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars

Class VariableSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.vars.VariableSource

  • public class VariableSource
extends java.lang.Object
    The class VariableSource describes exported variables of submodels either to define the connections among submodels when creating a coupled model or to define how a coupled model reexports the exported variables of its submodels.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant       name != null
 invariant       type != null
 invariant       exportingModelURI != null
